我看到他了
I see him.

6
00:02:31,290 --> 00:02:32,780
阿奇！
Kirill!

7
00:02:34,330 --> 00:02:35,450
该干活了
Time to work.

8
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:55,000
[国安局情报中心]
[维特山，维吉尼亚州]

9
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:20,930
零点三十分时，任务宣告失败
At 0030 hours, the mission deviated from the set parameters.

10
00:04:21,130 --> 00:04:24,930
探员被杀并不在计划之内
It wasn't part of the plan for our agent to get shot in the back.

11
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,770
身分确认
Identity confirmed.

12
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:35,410
麦格遇害时传送了一些资料
McGrath was uploading some data to us when he was killed.

13
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:38,880
你看看，我不确定这是什么
Take a look at this. I'm not sure yet exactly what it is.

14
00:04:41,820 --> 00:04:45,520
- 一个合成分子的部份  - 纪本
- A fragment of a complex molecule.  - Gibbons.

15
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:48,950
我们认为它跟前苏联生化武器…
We think it's a link to a Soviet bio-weapon...

16
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:50,820
“寂静之夜”有关
...called Silent Night.

17
00:04:51,060 --> 00:04:54,120
- 詹姆士，他怎么来了？ - 我找他来的
- James, what the hell is he doing here?  - I called him in.

18
00:04:54,330 --> 00:04:57,170
我们已损失三名探员，他帮得上忙
We've lost three agents already. You could use the help.

19
00:04:57,370 --> 00:05:00,640
狙杀探员的是“无政府99”
I found out your agents were killed by this group, Anarchy 99.

20
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:05,210
他们原是军人，能轻易辨识出训练有素的探员
They're ex-military. They can smell the training on our agents a mile away.

21
00:05:05,410 --> 00:05:09,440
我想我们该试试新方法了
Sir, I think it's time we tried something new.

22
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:21,230
这些不是我们的人，他们是谁？中情局的？
These guys aren't ours. Who are they? CIA?

23
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:25,660
是平民百姓，是罪犯、雇兵、杀手
No, civilians. Convicts, mercs, contract killers.

24
00:05:25,870 --> 00:05:28,130
社会底层最机灵也最强的份子
The best and brightest of the bottom of the barrel.

25
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:32,640
- 他们根本是人渣  - 他们好用、能牺牲又肯出力
- They're the scum of the earth.  - Programmable, expendable, effective.

26
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:35,570
我想这是最好的办法
I think it's our best shot.

27
00:05:35,780 --> 00:05:38,900
与其送羊入虎口
Do we want to drop another mouse in the snake pit?

28
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:42,480
还不如放只毒蛇去偷袭他们
Or send our own snake and let him crawl in?

29
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:45,800
[乡村俱乐部 非会员勿入]

30
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:49,350
[沙加缅度，加州]

31
00:05:51,690 --> 00:05:53,000
[玩滑板是犯罪]

32
00:05:53,330 --> 00:05:56,020
快点，小弟，真是的
Come on, Pepe. This is unbelievable.

33
00:05:56,730 --> 00:05:58,420
喂！
Hello!

34
00:05:58,630 --> 00:06:01,290
动作快点，听着
Well, it's about time. Now, listen....

35
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:04,660
你是哪里人？墨西哥？我没有恶意
Were you coming from Tijuana? I don't mean to be rude.

36
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:07,670
别停在太阳底下，烤漆会褪色
Keep it out of the sun. I don't want the paint to fade.

37
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:11,400
你听的懂英文吧？拿去，这够你花了
Do you understand English? I pay enough for you people.

38
00:06:15,550 --> 00:06:18,920
来吧，珍娜，你会喜欢这里的
Come on, Janelle. You're gonna love this place.

39
00:06:19,650 --> 00:06:22,490
- 迪克，你好  - 这是珍娜
- Dick, how are you?  - This is Janelle.

40
00:06:31,730 --> 00:06:33,390
- 快报警  - 开我车的人是谁？
- Call 911 .  - Who's driving my car?

41
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:42,210
我是霍议员，加州州议员
Senator Hotchkiss! California state Senate!

42
00:06:42,410 --> 00:06:44,670
听着，刚刚有人偷了我的车
Listen, somebody just stole my car!

43
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:13,100
红色敞篷车，立刻靠边停车
You, in the red Corvette! Pull over immediately!

44
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:17,800
是啊，条子追我，因为我偷了这车
Yeah, yeah. These monkeys are following me because I took this car.

45
00:07:18,010 --> 00:07:20,880
这车不是我的，它太花俏了
Obviously the car doesn't belong to me, it's not my style.

46
00:07:21,050 --> 00:07:26,350
它是迪克的车，霍迪克，加州州议员
It belongs to Dick, Dick Hotchkiss, a California state senator.

47
00:07:26,550 --> 00:07:29,490
就是他提案禁止饶舌歌曲…
You remember Dick. He tried to ban rap music...

48
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:32,720
因为他觉得饶舌歌鼓吹暴力
...because he feels the lyrics promote violence.

49
00:07:32,930 --> 00:07:34,260
那是音乐，迪克
It's music, Dick!

50
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:39,120
他也想提案禁止电玩…
He also wants to pull every video game off every shelf in the country...

51
00:07:39,330 --> 00:07:45,070
因为他觉得电玩退化了下一代的智能
...because he feels that the video games diminish the intelligence of our youth.

52
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:47,230
拜托，迪克
Come on, Dick.

53
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:50,240
那是我们唯一的教育啊
It's the only education we got.

54
00:07:52,610 --> 00:07:55,840
迪克，你是个坏蛋，我们对付坏蛋的方法
You're a bad man. You know what we do to bad men.

55
00:07:56,050 --> 00:07:57,520
就是处罚
We punish them.

56
00:07:57,750 --> 00:08:03,620
迪克，欢迎进入桑德特区
Dick, you've just entered the Xander zone.

57
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:07,250
我正带着一串条子往前冲
I'm coming in hot with a side of bacon!

58
00:08:16,070 --> 00:08:17,830
快、快啊
Go, go, go!

59
00:08:38,660 --> 00:08:39,750
快拉开
Pull it! Pull it!

60
00:09:00,380 --> 00:09:02,080
好耶
Yes!

61
00:09:27,510 --> 00:09:29,480
快去拿摄影机，快
Go get the cameras! Go! Go! Go!

62
00:09:34,410 --> 00:09:37,140
教训你做人别太过份，迪克
Moral is, don't be a dick, Dick!

63
00:09:43,290 --> 00:09:47,660
拿回摄影机了？好，走人
You guys got the cameras? All right, let's go, let's go!

64
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:55,030
再会啦
Peace out!

65
00:10:27,570 --> 00:10:29,590
厉害
Outstanding.

66
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,590
谢了
Thank you.

67
00:10:33,070 --> 00:10:35,270
- 你好  - 这些人是你请来的？
- What's up?  - You invited these people?

68
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,700
当然不是
Of course not.

69
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:43,410
好傢伙，你好啊
That's my dog! What's up?

70
00:10:43,620 --> 00:10:46,480
今天真是太棒了，你真猛
Today was off the hook! You're psycho, bro!

71
00:10:46,690 --> 00:10:49,450
猛？简直是帅呆了
Psycho? That was off the chain, man!

72
00:10:49,660 --> 00:10:54,820
你有耍出那个超炫的动作吗？
Yo, yo, yo! What's up with that crazy trick that we've been hearing about?

73
00:10:54,990 --> 00:10:58,290
- 蜘蛛人空中翻滚技？ - 当然
- My Superman seat-grab barrel roll?  - Word.

74
00:10:58,460 --> 00:11:00,960
我还在练习
I'm still working on it.

75
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:04,770
你真难找
You're a hard guy to get ahold of.

76
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:09,400
你这种运动员该要有专属电玩游戏
You know, an athlete like you should really have his own video game.

77
00:11:09,610 --> 00:11:13,200
金乔丹，我能帮你
Jordan King. I can make it happen.

78
00:11:13,850 --> 00:11:16,970
- 我以后会再跟你联络  - 没问题
- I'll hold on to this for later.  - You do that.

79
00:11:22,490 --> 00:11:25,580
他不会出卖自己的，他就是他
You know he'll never sell out. That's why he is who he is.

80
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:28,450
你别烦他了，是谁请你来的？
So you need to relax. Who invited you, anyway?

81
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:30,460
闭嘴
Shut up.

82
00:11:35,430 --> 00:11:39,270
听着，我是说真的，我能拿到网路预售的预付款
Listen, this is for real. I can get us an advance on Internet pre-sales.

83
00:11:39,470 --> 00:11:42,270
你只要去巴哥巴哥或哪里
So you need to just go to Pago Pago or something.

84
00:11:42,610 --> 00:11:45,600
找女人，我无所谓，去渡个假
Get some girls, do them all. I don't care. Go on vacation.

85
00:11:45,780 --> 00:11:49,440
是布拉布拉，这里的女人就够了
It's Bora Bora, J. I got enough girls here.

86
00:11:49,650 --> 00:11:52,450
你何时开始这么爱钱的？
Since when did you care so much about money?

87
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:55,640
我只是要你先避避锋头
I just need you to lay low till the heat's off, okay?

88
00:11:55,920 --> 00:12:00,790
我经营地下网站，我要卖录影带，但不要你坐牢
I run a secret website. I got tapes to make and I can't do that with you in jail.

89
00:12:00,990 --> 00:12:04,160
- 你看过了吗？ - 我不管，听我的话
- Did you see that?  - I don't care. Listen to me.

90
00:12:04,930 --> 00:12:05,990
我是无敌的
I'm untouchable.

91
00:12:15,740 --> 00:12:17,940
趴下！进去！快点
Let's go! Get out! Move!

92
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:20,010
好啦，我音乐会关小声一点
Okay, I'll turn down the music.

93
00:12:27,650 --> 00:12:30,050
不就一辆车而已吗？
It was only a Corvette.

94
00:12:34,590 --> 00:12:37,460
快点，菜都快凉了
Let's go, baby. Your order is getting cold.

95
00:12:42,370 --> 00:12:46,130
- 要来点咖啡吗？ - 给我来点炒马铃薯吧
- Want coffee?  - Can you give me some hash browns?

96
00:12:46,310 --> 00:12:49,930
- 好  - 别炒过头了，我喜欢软一点
- Sure.  - Make them sloppy. I like them runny.

97
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,040
我怎么会在这里？
How did I get here?

98
00:12:52,510 --> 00:12:56,970
两个大个子十分钟前丢下你，叫我好好照顾你
Two big guys dropped you off 10 minutes ago. Told me to look after you.

99
00:12:57,150 --> 00:12:59,780
来点咖啡？你看来很需要
You look like you could use some coffee.

100
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:17,500
你没事吧？
You all right?

101
00:13:17,700 --> 00:13:19,140
没事
Fine.

102
00:13:33,850 --> 00:13:37,290
干嘛？你有问题吗？
I said, you got a problem, boy?

103
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:38,990
没，没问题
No. No problem.

104
00:13:40,130 --> 00:13:42,390
- 大家不准动  - 不准动
- Nobody make a move!  - Nobody move!

105
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:47,000
想叫他去搬救兵？闭嘴
Just couldn't let him leave. Keep your goddamned mouth shut!

106
00:13:47,170 --> 00:13:51,430
- 别乱动，不然你死定了  - 把钱全拿出来，快
- Keep still or you'll stop breathing.  - Empty the goddamn register!

107
00:13:56,410 --> 00:13:58,070
退后
Get back!

108
00:13:58,380 --> 00:14:00,070
退后、退后
Get back. Get back!

109
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:09,680
- 漂亮，大明星  - 你是谁？
- Well done, Mr. Cage.  - Who the hell are you?

110
00:14:10,160 --> 00:14:13,920
纪本，奥纪本
The name's Gibbons. Augustus Gibbons.

111
00:14:14,260 --> 00:14:16,790
你似乎很不爽，怎么了？
You seem upset. Is there a problem?

112
00:14:17,060 --> 00:14:19,500
- 这是什么地方？ - 看起来是餐厅
- What is this place?  - Looks like a diner.

113
00:14:19,900 --> 00:14:21,800
答的真好
That's clever.

114
00:14:22,570 --> 00:14:25,470
你差一点就骗倒我了
You almost had me going there for a while.

115
00:14:25,670 --> 00:14:29,800
一开始我有点头昏，后来我开始注意到一些事
I was a bit groggy before, then I started noticing things.

116
00:14:31,010 --> 00:14:34,070
那里坐了个衣冠楚楚的分析师…
Like, you got a stockbroker over here, all dressed up...

117
00:14:34,250 --> 00:14:39,450
看工商时报，在股市休市的星期天早上
...reading the Financial Times on Sunday when the market's closed.

118
00:14:39,650 --> 00:14:43,050
不太合理，但我还可以接受
Unlikely, but okay, I can go with that.

119
00:14:43,260 --> 00:14:47,320
我也能接受这个抢匪用警用的制式手枪
I could even go with the stick-up man packing a cop-issue Beretta.

120
00:14:47,490 --> 00:14:51,550
知道最大的问题出在哪里吗？就是她
But you want to know where you blew it? With her.

121
00:14:51,900 --> 00:14:54,730
我舅妈在餐厅工作了一辈子
My aunt was in the restaurant business.

122
00:14:54,900 --> 00:14:59,300
专职女服务生绝不会穿高跟鞋
There's no way a career waitress comes to work in high heels.

123
00:14:59,510 --> 00:15:02,070
那样她的脚铁定会长水泡
She'd have blisters the size of pancakes.

124
00:15:02,410 --> 00:15:05,940
而如果她是假扮的，那这整个场景就是假的
And if she ain't real, then this whole thing ain't real.

125
00:15:06,180 --> 00:15:09,640
所以我知道这场戏再怎么演…
That's how I knew that this bozo wouldn't get a shot off...

126
00:15:09,850 --> 00:15:12,720
这笨蛋也绝不会开枪
...even if we waited till St. Patrick's Day.

127
00:15:14,850 --> 00:15:17,880
因为枪里只有空包弹
Because there's nothing but blanks in these guns.

128
00:15:18,890 --> 00:15:22,690
对了，我无意挑剔…
Oh, and no offense...

129
00:15:23,530 --> 00:15:27,230
但他们的演技真是够烂
...but their performances were terrible.

130
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:36,600
很好，非常好
That's good. That's very good.

131
00:15:36,780 --> 00:15:39,870
该你了，大帅哥
It's your turn, pretty boy.

132
00:15:41,750 --> 00:15:45,880
- 这到底是怎么回事？ - 这是测验，你高分通过了
- What the hell is going on here?  - lt was a test that you aced.

133
00:15:46,490 --> 00:15:50,550
- 他的态度不太好  - 什么？
- He seems to have a poor attitude.  - Excuse me?

134
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:54,350
- 要不要把他扔回去？ - 不，我喜欢他的态度
- Should we throw him back?  - Hell, no. I love his attitude.

135
00:15:54,530 --> 00:15:57,520
进行下一步，快去联络
Let's take this to the next level. Get on the Sat-Com.

136
00:15:57,700 --> 00:15:59,860
什么下一步？
Take what to the next level?

137
00:16:00,070 --> 00:16:03,230
- 什么下一步？ - 全员十分钟内离去
- Yo! Take what?  - I want everybody out in 10 minutes.

138
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:06,270
我不奉陪
I don't play this game.

139
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:09,930
- 送麦克就医，否则他脸就毁了  - 我还要回派对去
- Get Mike a doctor or he'll look like me.  - I got a party.

140
00:16:10,110 --> 00:16:12,580
- 让他闭嘴  - 别忘了赔我窗户的钱
- Shut him up.  - And pay for my windows!

141
00:16:19,950 --> 00:16:23,850
怎么通过测验的老是些烂人？
Why is it always the assholes who pass the tests?

142
00:16:46,950 --> 00:16:50,440
你们最近不会都到过餐厅吧？
You guys haven't been to any diners lately, huh?

143
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:54,480
餐厅胜出者
Diner finalists.

144
00:17:02,130 --> 00:17:04,890
- 怎么，没咖啡啊？ - 好耶
- What, no coffee?  - Oh, yeah.

145
00:17:05,060 --> 00:17:07,290
- 指挥军官在此  - 开始了
- Here comes the ROTC.  - Here we go.

146
00:17:08,630 --> 00:17:10,970
- 我的花生米呢？ - 酷啊
- Where's my peanuts?  - Nice.

147
00:17:12,670 --> 00:17:14,640
帮我叫空姐过来一下吧
Can you ask for the stewardess?

148
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:22,940
- 预备放减速伞  - 知道了，减速伞预备
- Standing by to deploy drogue.  - Roger, deploying drogue parachute.

149
00:17:32,060 --> 00:17:33,990
- 这会很痛  - 这是在搞什么？
- This will hurt.  - What the hell?

150
00:17:48,510 --> 00:17:50,700
- 放出减速伞  - 知道了
- Release drogue now.  - Roger.

151
00:17:52,750 --> 00:17:55,040
这不好吧
This ain't right!

152
00:17:55,210 --> 00:17:56,910
这算不了什么！
I live for this shit!

153
00:18:15,730 --> 00:18:17,400
不赖嘛
Not bad!

154
00:18:19,770 --> 00:18:21,470
再来一次吧
Let's do that again!

155
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:38,650
靠，这里是哥伦比亚
Holy shit. This is Colombia.

156
00:18:38,820 --> 00:18:41,880
可卡因，这些都是可卡因树
Cocaine, man. These are coke plants!

157
00:18:47,730 --> 00:18:49,130
没钥匙
No keys.

158
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:55,170
- 你在干嘛？ - 这些可值钱了
- What the hell are you doing?  - You know what this shit's worth?

159
00:18:57,240 --> 00:19:00,110
怎么？测验人员来了？
What now? Is this another test?

160
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:03,580
- 我们过河去，快  - 是啊，快跑吧
- Let's go across the river. Let's go!  - Yeah, good idea! Good idea!

161
00:19:11,760 --> 00:19:15,280
你们真是比我强太多了，我想我测验不及格了
You monkeys are too good for me. I failed this test.

162
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:20,430
你们有带喝的吗？
You guys got something to drink?

163
00:19:32,980 --> 00:19:34,950
真高兴又见面了
Nice to see you again, fellas.

164
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:36,880
是啊
Yeah, you too.

165
00:19:37,780 --> 00:19:40,450
他们这回可真是大费周章
Boy, they went all out on this one.

166
00:20:08,980 --> 00:20:10,470
不会吧？
You've got to be kidding.

167
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:19,560
好了，笨蛋
Okay, funny guys.

168
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:23,560
见识一下我们怎么处置入侵者吧
I'll show you what we do when you get in our business.

169
00:20:24,030 --> 00:20:28,260
绑住我们，逼我们听你讲话？
What? Hog-tie us and force us to listen to your bad accent?

170
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:30,330
不
No.

171
00:20:30,900 --> 00:20:36,000
我们砍断他们的脚筋看着他们痛苦挣扎
We cut their Achilles tendon and watch them flop around like a marionette.

172
00:20:36,180 --> 00:20:40,910
除非你有话跟我说重要的情报
Unless you have something to tell me, something I need to know?

173
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:43,610
好吧，你很矮
Okay. You're short.

174
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:50,580
我朋友说你可以去换个发型，放开我
My friend says you could use a haircut to update your style. Get off me.

175
00:20:52,520 --> 00:20:54,050
闭嘴
Shut up!

176
00:20:54,630 --> 00:20:58,190
你刚刚才叫我们讲话，现在却要闭嘴？
Two seconds ago you told us to talk. Now it's "Shut up?"

177
00:20:58,360 --> 00:21:02,660
我无意挑剔，但你真不会逼供
I don't mean to nitpick, but you're the worst at this torture thing.

178
00:21:05,140 --> 00:21:08,440
你再打我，我就扁死你
You slap me again, I'm going to throw you a beating.

179
00:21:14,410 --> 00:21:16,940
希望你这样有领比较多酬劳
I hope they're paying you extra for this.

180
00:21:17,380 --> 00:21:21,440
这样吧，也许我该先割了你的鼻子
You know what, funny guy? Maybe I'll cut off your nose first.

181
00:21:21,620 --> 00:21:24,020
笨蛋
Funny guy.

182
00:21:24,190 --> 00:21:28,890
怪了，这上面有真正的血腥味
What's funny is, this actually smells like real blood.

183
00:21:30,230 --> 00:21:34,390
希望你喜欢，这会是你最后闻到的东西了
I hope you like it, because it's the last thing you're going to smell.

184
00:21:59,360 --> 00:22:02,050
我中枪了
I'm hit! I'm hit! I'm hit!

185
00:22:08,630 --> 00:22:10,100
维多，快帮忙
Virg! Give me a hand.

186
00:22:21,550 --> 00:22:22,540
我们是哥伦比亚政府军
This is the Colombian army!

187
00:22:22,710 --> 00:22:24,340
快投降，你们已被包围！
Give up, you're surrounded!

188
00:22:29,120 --> 00:22:31,320
自己走，小杰
Try to walk, T.J. Try to walk.

189
00:22:31,520 --> 00:22:33,290
维多，快走
Virg! Get out here!

190
00:22:34,630 --> 00:22:37,960
去他的，人不为己天诛地灭
To hell with this. Every man for himself.

191
00:23:00,650 --> 00:23:02,590
我去找交通工具
I'll get us some wheels.

192
00:23:03,390 --> 00:23:04,880
在这等着
Hang in there.

193
00:23:05,120 --> 00:23:06,110
祝好运
Good luck.

194
00:24:19,100 --> 00:24:21,790
那个骑机车的就是毒枭！
The guy on the bike, that's the drug lord!

195
00:24:22,070 --> 00:24:23,300
快逮住他！
Let's get him!

196
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:41,910
小杰
T.J.!

197
00:25:59,230 --> 00:26:02,060
X，我在这里
X! I'm over here! X!

198
00:26:21,190 --> 00:26:22,850
他在那里！
There he is!

199
00:27:30,120 --> 00:27:32,150
我们把他烤焦了！
We toasted his ass!

200
00:27:43,670 --> 00:27:44,860
我弄了一辆机车
I got us a bike.

201
00:27:50,980 --> 00:27:52,710
胆小鬼！
Pussies!

202
00:28:00,690 --> 00:28:06,590
看谁来了，科学怪人，打开我的手铐，我要扁死你
Look who it is. Frankenstein. Uncuff me so I can beat the shit out of you.

203
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:10,060
别激动，你刚以第一名毕业
Relax, X, you just graduated at the head of your class.

204
00:28:10,230 --> 00:28:13,890
你在胡说什么？你差点害死我们
What are you talking about? You almost got us killed.

205
00:28:14,070 --> 00:28:16,590
- 我们知道哥国军队正在逼近  - 什么？
- We knew the army was moving.  - Excuse me?

206
00:28:16,770 --> 00:28:20,400
是我建议拿你当诱饵，怎样？
It was my idea to send you as a decoy. How do you like that?

207
00:28:24,940 --> 00:28:27,940
- 你真是个身手矫健的老人  - 起来
- You're pretty fast for an old man.  - Get up.

208
00:28:30,950 --> 00:28:32,540
陪我走一走
Walk with me.

209
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:38,980
我相信只要有好的环境，人是会改变的
I believe under the right circumstances, a man can change.

210
00:28:39,190 --> 00:28:43,060
举例来说，昨晚你展现了勇气、领导能力…
For instance, last night you exhibited courage, leadership...

211
00:28:43,230 --> 00:28:45,860
还愿意保护一个陌生人
...and willingness to protect a man you hardly knew.

212
00:28:46,030 --> 00:28:49,360
- 颁个勋章给我好了  - 我宁可给你一份工作
- So give me a medal.  - I'd rather give you a job.

213
00:28:49,730 --> 00:28:53,570
你看看我，我看来像是执法人员吗？
Look at me. Do I look like a fan of law enforcement?

214
00:28:53,870 --> 00:28:56,070
今天是你的幸运日
This is your lucky day, Xander.

215
00:28:56,240 --> 00:28:58,970
你有机会可以报答国家…
This is your chance to pay your Uncle Sam...

216
00:28:59,140 --> 00:29:01,370
感谢它让你享受自由
...for all your wonderful freedoms.

217
00:29:01,550 --> 00:29:03,380
工作本身并不难
The job's not that difficult.

218
00:29:03,580 --> 00:29:07,210
我只是要你去见一些人，查明他们的底细
I want you to meet people and find out what you can about them.

219
00:29:07,390 --> 00:29:09,080
那一种人？
What type of people?

220
00:29:09,250 --> 00:29:14,520
危险、下流、野蛮，你们那种人
Dangerous, dirty, tattooed, uncivilized. Your kind of people.

221
00:29:15,790 --> 00:29:17,230
等等
Hold up.

222
00:29:18,230 --> 00:29:22,890
我这种人会说“去你的，大花脸”
My kind of people would say, "Kiss my ass, scarface."

223
00:29:24,070 --> 00:29:27,230
此时我通常会拔枪相向，再礼貌的…
Usually I'd take my gun, press it to your temple...

224
00:29:27,410 --> 00:29:30,430
请你照我的话去做
...and ask you very politely to do what I want.

225
00:29:30,610 --> 00:29:34,200
但你并不怕死，这让我们陷入了窘境
But you're not afraid of death. That puts us in a quandary.

226
00:29:34,410 --> 00:29:37,900
- 我想讨论就到此结束了  - 还没
- We better call this a day, then.  - Not just yet.

227
00:29:39,150 --> 00:29:42,020
你看过动物园里的狮子吗？
You ever watch lions at the zoo?

228
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:47,350
透过它们的眼睛，你就能分辨哪只是野生的
You can tell which were captured in the wild by the look in their eyes.

229
00:29:47,530 --> 00:29:48,620
大野猫
The wild cat.

230
00:29:49,430 --> 00:29:52,790
它记得奔驰草原的快乐、猎杀的快感
She remembers running across the plain, the thrill of the hunt.

231
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:56,900
四百磅的猎杀高手，被关着
Four hundred pounds of killing fury locked in a box.

232
00:29:57,640 --> 00:30:00,400
过一阵子，它们眼神变得呆滞…
But after a while, their eyes glaze over...

233
00:30:00,710 --> 00:30:03,500
你看得出它的灵魂已死
...and you can tell their soul has died.

234
00:30:04,010 --> 00:30:06,200
人也是一样
The same thing happens to a man.

235
00:30:06,410 --> 00:30:09,070
联邦监狱可不是儿童乐园
Leavenworth Federal Penitentiary is no joke.

236
00:30:09,250 --> 00:30:13,270
他们会把你这种狂人丢进单人牢房取乐
They'll take a wild man and throw him in solitary just for fun.

237
00:30:13,690 --> 00:30:19,020
不再有山可爬，不再有浪可冲
No more mountains to board, no more oceans to surf.

238
00:30:19,190 --> 00:30:24,490
只有一个小牢房，不见天日，只有一个粪桶
Just a 6-by-8 cell with no window and only a bucket to shit in.

239
00:30:25,360 --> 00:30:28,060
但你只要帮个忙，就能免去一切
You can avoid that by doing me this favor.

240
00:30:28,230 --> 00:30:30,360
你根本没有我的把柄
You don't have shit on me.

241
00:30:30,540 --> 00:30:34,490
我注意到你的后颈有三个“X”的刺青
I noticed you have three X's tattooed on the back of your neck.

242
00:30:35,870 --> 00:30:40,280
我觉得那满适合你的，因为你背负三项罪名
I think that's rather appropriate since you're looking at three strikes.

243
00:30:40,450 --> 00:30:45,080
偷车、危害公安，还有你那个跳桥特技…
Grand theft, reckless endangerment, and that bridge stunt of yours...

244
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:47,650
让你彻底输了三次
...makes you a three-time loser.

245
00:30:47,820 --> 00:30:50,790
也许你该自称为“XXX”
Maybe you ought to call yourself "Triple X."

246
00:30:51,790 --> 00:30:56,450
但如果你照我的话去做，我就让你无罪开释
But if you do what I want, I'll make all your transgressions go away...

247
00:30:56,630 --> 00:31:00,260
让你回去过你那可笑的生活
...and let you get back to that pathetic excuse of a life.

248
00:31:02,300 --> 00:31:05,000
或者你认为我该跟你一样
Or you think maybe I should be like you.

249
00:31:06,270 --> 00:31:09,400
被打个脸上开花
Get all shot up for the old Stars and Stripes.

250
00:31:09,870 --> 00:31:14,310
你每回照镜子时一定很自傲
I bet that flag is a real comfort every time you look in the mirror.

251
00:31:14,480 --> 00:31:19,350
这只是个我为国付出的小代价
A small price I paid for putting foot to ass for my country.

252
00:31:24,060 --> 00:31:26,820
怎么样，XXX？
So, what's it going to be, Triple X?

253
00:31:26,990 --> 00:31:29,480
你想立刻上路…
You want to get on a plane...

254
00:31:29,660 --> 00:31:34,360
还是给我一句“去你的，大花脸”？
...or is "Kiss my ass, scarface" your final answer?

255
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:47,700
[布拉格，捷克]

256
00:32:03,230 --> 00:32:05,090
你叫什么名字？
Yo. What's your name, slick?

257
00:32:05,260 --> 00:32:06,560
我叫伊凡
My name is lvan.

258
00:32:06,730 --> 00:32:10,900
- 伊凡？那你呢？ - 我叫伊凡
- lvan? What's your name, buddy?  - My name is lvan.

259
00:32:11,070 --> 00:32:12,800
你们都叫伊凡？
You're both lvan?

260
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:43,860
坐下
Take a seat.

261
00:32:44,600 --> 00:32:47,300
笨蛋，美国探员呢？
Idiots! Where is the American agent?

262
00:32:47,470 --> 00:32:48,560
这就是了
This is him, Sir.

263
00:32:50,180 --> 00:32:52,800
我们最好再订个装尸袋
We better order another bodybag.

264
00:32:53,610 --> 00:32:55,550
有什么事吗？
Guys, what's up?

265
00:32:57,180 --> 00:32:58,550
我叫你坐下
I told you to sit down.

266
00:32:58,980 --> 00:33:02,750
我在飞机上坐半天了，我想站
I've just been on a plane for 12 hours. I think I'll stand.

267
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:06,120
我是苏米兰，捷克秘密警察
My name is Milan Sova, Czech secret police.

268
00:33:06,290 --> 00:33:08,850
你到这里，就得受我管辖
Here, you are under my jurisdiction.

269
00:33:09,030 --> 00:33:11,460
你听我的命令，照我的话去做
You take my orders, you do what I say.

270
00:33:11,630 --> 00:33:15,120
如果你变得碍手碍脚，我就杀了你
If you become any kind of an inconvenience, I'll shoot you.

271
00:33:15,570 --> 00:33:18,200
很好，我就住这？
That's great. Is this where I'm staying?

272
00:33:18,370 --> 00:33:21,630
你会在此是因你的政府逼我们
Your government is putting pressure on mine.

273
00:33:21,810 --> 00:33:25,710
这是一桩国内事务，你们这是干涉捷克内政
This is an internal Czech affair that you are interfering with.

274
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:28,850
我警告你，别在我家撒野
I will warn you once: Don't shit in my lawn.

275
00:33:29,010 --> 00:33:33,710
取得你们政府想要的情报后，就快点滚
Get whatever information your government seeks and get out.

276
00:33:34,150 --> 00:33:35,680
明人不说暗话
Let's get this straight.

277
00:33:35,850 --> 00:33:39,590
你也许不想让我来，而我根本也不想来
You may not want me here, but I definitely don't want to be here.

278
00:33:39,790 --> 00:33:43,160
再说，我没受任何人管辖过
Two, I've never been under anyone's jurisdiction.

279
00:33:43,830 --> 00:33:46,190
第三，如果你想杀人…
Three, if you're going to shoot anybody...

280
00:33:46,430 --> 00:33:48,990
去杀卖这套衣服给你的人吧
...shoot that monkey that sold you the suit.

281
00:33:49,170 --> 00:33:51,730
我很累，我要睡了
Now, I'm tired. I'm going to sleep.

282
00:33:53,710 --> 00:33:56,270
三小时后出发
Be ready in three hours.

283
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:03,680
俱乐部里的人有两个共通点：
Everybody in this club has two things in common:

284
00:34:03,850 --> 00:34:09,910
- 他们都很有钱，也都是罪犯  - 我绝对合适，只是我并不有钱
- They're rich and they're criminals.  - I'll fit in, except for the rich part.

285
00:34:24,300 --> 00:34:27,830
- 记住，我们互不相识  - 真希望是如此
- Remember, we don't know each other.  - I wish we didn't.

286
00:34:42,050 --> 00:34:44,540
给我来杯红莓苏打
Yeah, can I get a cranberry club soda?

287
00:34:45,590 --> 00:34:49,220
这放后面，我会给你小费
Throw this back there? I'll tip you something.

288
00:34:49,390 --> 00:34:51,590
就放后面
Put it in the back.

289
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:55,900
这要多少？有存根吗？
How much? Do I get a ticket?

290
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:04,070
他们在那里，“无政府99”
That's them. Anarchy 99.

291
00:35:04,240 --> 00:35:06,110
看见坐在中间沙发那个人了？
You see the guy on the couch?

292
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:08,750
那就是尤里，他是老大
That's Yorgi. He's the leader.

293
00:35:08,910 --> 00:35:13,580
他拥有六间这样的俱乐部，全都是金鸡母
He owns this club and five others like it. All, how do you say, cash cows.

294
00:35:13,750 --> 00:35:15,240
美国佬？！
American?!

295
00:35:18,120 --> 00:35:21,320
我是美国人，我要见尤里，尤里？！
Guys, I'm American. I'm going to see Yorgi. Yorgi!

296
00:35:21,560 --> 00:35:23,860
尤里，听说你就是
Hey, Yorgi! I hear you're the guy...

297
00:35:27,700 --> 00:35:29,930
我听说可以找你买车
I heard you're the guy to talk to about cars.

298
00:35:30,300 --> 00:35:31,530
请你出去
Take yourself outside.

299
00:35:32,040 --> 00:35:34,300
出去？我才刚…
Take myself outside? I'm just...

300
00:35:36,140 --> 00:35:38,730
好吧，我不受欢迎
Okay. I'm not welcome.

301
00:35:38,910 --> 00:35:41,470
也许你宁愿条子进你的俱乐部
Guess you'd rather have cops in your club.

302
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:45,870
想谈谈吗？
Want to talk?

303
00:35:46,380 --> 00:35:49,980
过来告诉我哪个是条子…
Hey, you silly boy. Come with me and show me the cop...

304
00:35:50,190 --> 00:35:52,180
别弄错了
...and don't be mistake.

305
00:35:52,420 --> 00:35:55,760
看到那个傢伙了？穿的很蠢的那个
See that guy there, with the suit made out of drapes?

306
00:35:55,930 --> 00:35:57,660
那个就是条子
That's a cop.

307
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:06,000
怎么了？我才刚喝一杯
Is there a problem? I just had a drink, you know?

308
00:36:06,440 --> 00:36:11,170
我付过钱了，我会给很大一笔小费的
I already paid. I'm going to give a big tip, you know?

309
00:36:17,520 --> 00:36:20,970
这是干嘛？我什么都没做啊
So, what is this all about? I've done nothing.

310
00:36:21,390 --> 00:36:24,690
什么都没做？你是做什么的？
You've done nothing? Who do you work for?

311
00:36:25,790 --> 00:36:28,160
我在银行工作，怎么？
I work in a bank. So what?

312
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:30,420
少扯了…
You've got to be....

313
00:36:31,100 --> 00:36:34,430
你干嘛？住手
What are you doing? Stop it! Stop it!

314
00:36:36,630 --> 00:36:38,930
这是什么？学生证吗？
What's that, your bus pass?

315
00:36:39,100 --> 00:36:41,970
捷克警察、捷克警察
Czech 5-0. Czech 5-0.

316
00:36:44,380 --> 00:36:45,430
给我离开
Leave my club.

317
00:36:48,810 --> 00:36:50,250
你怎么知道的？
How did you know?

318
00:36:50,420 --> 00:36:55,720
我怎么知道？他付钱的时候，警徽反光差点害我瞎掉
When he was paying for his drinks, he was flashing his badge to half the bar.

319
00:36:55,890 --> 00:36:57,080
条子跟蟑螂一样
Cops like plague.

320
00:36:57,260 --> 00:37:01,250
不管收买多少，总还有人要钱
No matter how many you pay, there's always another with his hand out.

321
00:37:01,460 --> 00:37:03,890
我也是混道上的，我暸解
I'm from the streets. I know cops, believe me.

322
00:37:04,060 --> 00:37:08,800
我很感谢你引起我们注意，问题是为什么？
I appreciate you bringing this to our attention. My question to you is why?

323
00:37:09,230 --> 00:37:12,130
我想没人喜欢条子混进来
I figure, no one likes cops crashing their party.

324
00:37:12,300 --> 00:37:15,070
我想我帮你忙，就能说上话
I figure, I do you a solid, we could talk.

325
00:37:16,570 --> 00:37:19,100
我想买车
I just want to buy cars, man.

326
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:22,670
这傢伙是不是想上我？
Is this guy going to hump my leg?

327
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:25,810
你叫什么名字？
What's your name?

328
00:37:28,420 --> 00:37:29,720
桑德凯吉
Xander Cage.

329
00:37:31,820 --> 00:37:33,350
我就知道
I knew it.

