00:51:56,080 --> 00:51:58,600
谁的政治？不是我们的
Whose politics? Not ours!

493
00:51:58,780 --> 00:52:02,910
所以我们当下决定，从此要为所欲为
So we decide from then on to do what we want, when we want.

494
00:52:03,080 --> 00:52:07,420
为纪念他们，我们自称“无政府99”
It is in their honor we call ourselves Anarchy 99.

495
00:52:13,130 --> 00:52:16,290
有首老庞克歌曲，歌词说：
You know, there's an old punk song. It says:

496
00:52:16,460 --> 00:52:18,620
美国代表自由
The United States on behalf of freedom

497
00:52:18,830 --> 00:52:20,360
但你若自以为自由
But if you think you're free

498
00:52:20,530 --> 00:52:23,830
去趟小吃店，在小菜上撒泡尿
Go to the snack bar, Piss on the side dishes

499
00:52:24,000 --> 00:52:26,770
- 你知道！ - 汪达合唱团的“无政府汉堡”
- You got it!  - "Anarchy Burger" by the Vandals.

500
00:52:28,610 --> 00:52:31,270
我赞成你，但你要怎么做？
I'm with you, but what are you going to do?

501
00:52:31,440 --> 00:52:36,210
到处都有法规、都有政府，以前有，以后也会一直有
You got rules and government everywhere. Always was, always will be.

502
00:52:36,380 --> 00:52:38,180
也许不会一直有
Maybe not always.

503
00:52:44,560 --> 00:52:47,150
别让他寂寞
Make sure he doesn't get lonely.

504
00:52:47,460 --> 00:52:49,120
放开一点
Don't be shy.

505
00:52:57,240 --> 00:52:59,030
想跳舞吗？
You want to dance?

506
00:53:05,010 --> 00:53:06,480
喂，喂！
Hey. Hey!

507
00:53:13,320 --> 00:53:16,810
喂！我舞技很棒的
Hey! I'm really a good dancer.

508
00:53:21,830 --> 00:53:23,390
来两杯
Make that two.

509
00:53:25,030 --> 00:53:27,300
好吧，你打算一直这样对我？
All right, it's going to be like that?

510
00:53:28,840 --> 00:53:31,900
你气他，也别拿我出气啊
If you're mad at him, don't take it out on me.

511
00:53:32,510 --> 00:53:36,670
我一直在想你们俩的关系
I've been trying to figure out the deal between you two all night.

512
00:53:37,280 --> 00:53:38,970
你是他的女人？
You his woman or what?

513
00:53:39,950 --> 00:53:44,510
对，我是，若付我一样多钱，我也能跟你
Yeah, I'm his woman. If you pay me as much, I'll be your woman too.

514
00:54:35,500 --> 00:54:39,060
- 你喜欢吗？ - 喜欢
- Did you enjoy that?  - Yeah.

515
00:54:39,240 --> 00:54:42,170
很好，因为它不会再发生了
Good, because it will never happen again.

516
00:55:40,630 --> 00:55:44,870
原来的堡主有一天决定落跑
The original owners just one day decide to move out.

517
00:55:46,040 --> 00:55:48,870
- 这里真棒  - 请不要拘礼
- This is amazing, man.  - Make yourself at home.

518
00:55:55,010 --> 00:55:56,880
我帮你拿外套
Let me get your coat.

519
00:56:04,520 --> 00:56:07,320
那小子怎么了？他喜欢外套？
What's up with your boy? He got a coat fetish?

520
00:56:07,490 --> 00:56:09,220
不
Oh, no.

521
00:56:09,400 --> 00:56:13,460
他爱上她了，笨蛋
He's in love with her. Dirty fool.

522
00:56:25,210 --> 00:56:29,170
该上床了，天快亮了，约娜！
Time for bed, X. It's getting early. Yelena!

523
00:56:30,280 --> 00:56:32,440
你带他去他的房间吧
Would you kindly show him his room?

524
00:56:49,640 --> 00:56:51,230
- 你先请  - 不，你先
- After you.  - No, after you.

525
00:56:51,400 --> 00:56:54,170
- 不，你先  - 不，我坚持
- No, after you.  - No, I insist.

526
00:56:59,480 --> 00:57:00,570
这里就是了
That's it.

527
00:57:03,220 --> 00:57:05,620
跟我上床的最后一次机会
Last chance to tuck me in.

528
00:57:07,390 --> 00:57:08,820
祝你好梦
Good morning.

529
00:57:58,470 --> 00:58:01,770
我要为国奋战一番
The things I'm going to do for my country.

530
00:59:32,930 --> 00:59:36,100
这不关我的事，但是用电钻…
It's none of my business, but a power drill and some titanium bits...

531
00:59:36,270 --> 00:59:38,070
会比用相机有用多了
...will get you a lot further than that camera.

532
00:59:38,240 --> 00:59:40,470
你不该在这里的
You're not supposed to be in here.

533
00:59:40,640 --> 00:59:42,730
我本来是想去上厕所
I was on my way to the bathroom.

534
00:59:45,210 --> 00:59:47,110
你的藉口呢？
What's your excuse?

535
00:59:47,810 --> 00:59:49,800
我不需要藉口
I don't need an excuse.

536
00:59:52,590 --> 00:59:53,980
你真行
Oh, you're good.

537
00:59:55,590 --> 00:59:57,320
但还不够行
But not that good.

538
00:59:57,490 --> 01:00:00,820
我是来拍摄尤里的保险箱
I came in here to photograph Yorgi's safe.

539
01:00:00,990 --> 01:00:03,660
因为我觉得它可能很值钱
I thought it might be worth a lot to somebody.

540
01:00:03,830 --> 01:00:07,530
拜托，你冷血、聪明又危险
Come on. You're cold, intelligent and vicious.

541
01:00:09,600 --> 01:00:11,700
你的眼神泄露了你的身分
It's your eyes that give you away.

542
01:00:13,040 --> 01:00:15,670
就在我射杀那条子的时候
They gave you away when I shot that cop.

543
01:00:18,310 --> 01:00:20,240
你现在打算怎么做？
What are you going to do now?

544
01:00:24,450 --> 01:00:27,180
我现在要请你吃午餐
Now I'm going to take you to lunch.

545
01:00:28,950 --> 01:00:32,450
还有，我杀的那个条子，他没死
Oh, and that cop I shot, isn't dead.

546
01:00:53,080 --> 01:00:55,570
我有情报要给你
I have some information for you.

547
01:00:57,420 --> 01:01:02,410
我一直都用得上情报，你是谁？你怎会有我的号码？
I can always use information. Who is this? How did you get this number?

548
01:01:03,490 --> 01:01:08,830
关于桑德凯吉的重要情报
Yes. Important information that you need about Xander Cage.

549
01:01:19,000 --> 01:01:23,240
- 你不喜欢外国人？ - 没错，你是一只猪
- So you don't like foreigners, do you?  - No, you're a pig.

550
01:01:24,540 --> 01:01:26,600
你的相好呢？他也是猪？
Is your boyfriend a pig too?

551
01:01:26,780 --> 01:01:29,370
你应该认得你的同类啊
You should recognize one of your kind.

552
01:01:29,550 --> 01:01:31,380
告诉我条子的事
Now, tell me about the cop.

553
01:01:33,620 --> 01:01:37,110
若我说我跟你想像的不一样，你会怎么说？
What if I told you I'm not who you think I am?

554
01:01:38,460 --> 01:01:40,450
我可以帮你解决你的问题
That I could get you out of the mess you're in?

555
01:01:40,630 --> 01:01:42,890
是吗？我有什么问题？
Really? And what mess am I in?

556
01:01:43,060 --> 01:01:48,160
它让你趁大家熟睡时，蹑手蹑脚刺探情报
The mess that makes you sneak around the castle when everyone's asleep.

557
01:01:48,330 --> 01:01:49,430
条子的事呢？
The cop?

558
01:01:52,570 --> 01:01:56,340
你看这个，这叫镇静喷血弹
See this? It's called a blood-splatter dart.

559
01:01:56,510 --> 01:02:00,810
撞击很真实，但却无害，主要是红色颜料
The impact's real, but it's harmless. Red paint, mostly.

560
01:02:02,720 --> 01:02:03,700
为什么？
Why?

561
01:02:05,650 --> 01:02:07,140
我是个情报员
I'm a secret agent.

562
01:02:14,060 --> 01:02:16,820
你这不是在糗我吗？
Are you sure you don't want to embarrass me?

563
01:02:17,400 --> 01:02:19,800
- 拜托  - 有这么好笑吗？
- Come on.  - What's so funny about that?

564
01:02:21,400 --> 01:02:23,660
你看看你
I mean, look at you.

565
01:02:23,940 --> 01:02:26,430
我隶属于美国国安局
I work for the NSA.

566
01:02:29,010 --> 01:02:31,100
你真会搞笑
You're funny, you know that?

567
01:02:35,280 --> 01:02:36,980
约娜，我是阿奇
Yelena, it's Kirill.

568
01:02:37,550 --> 01:02:41,350
尤里发现凯吉是美国情报员
Yorgi found out that Cage is an American agent.

569
01:02:42,020 --> 01:02:46,980
你知道我在说什么吗？你有危险，亲爱的
Do you understand what I'm telling you? You are in danger, my love.

570
01:02:47,690 --> 01:02:50,360
对街的大楼，雕像后面
The building across the street. The statue.

571
01:02:51,730 --> 01:02:54,930
带他出来，其他的由我来
Bring him outside. I will do the rest.

572
01:03:01,810 --> 01:03:04,140
是谁？你的相好？
What was that, your boyfriend?

573
01:03:10,320 --> 01:03:13,840
假设你说的是真的
Let's say you are who you say you are.

574
01:03:15,450 --> 01:03:18,550
- 你能帮我做些什么？ - 你想要什么？
- What can you do for me?  - What do you want?

575
01:03:19,890 --> 01:03:25,230
我要免诉权，美国给我庇护和公民身分
I want immunity from prosecution, asylum in the U.S. and citizenship.

576
01:03:25,560 --> 01:03:27,960
住迈阿密，外加有钱男友一个？
How about a condo on South Beach and a rich boyfriend?

577
01:03:28,130 --> 01:03:30,190
那些我自己来就行
Those I can get for myself.

578
01:03:31,570 --> 01:03:34,770
- 你要我怎么做？ - 我要知道“无政府99”的详情
- What do you want?  - I need to know more about Anarchy 99.

579
01:03:35,110 --> 01:03:37,440
你想知道详情？
You want to know about Anarchy 99?

580
01:03:38,210 --> 01:03:41,650
你看到辣妹、俱乐部和派对了
You've seen the girls, the clubs, the parties.

581
01:03:41,810 --> 01:03:45,550
但你看不到白天发生的事
What you don't see is what goes on during the day.

582
01:03:46,150 --> 01:03:51,250
去年活动很频繁，人们进进出出的
There's been a lot of activity in the last year. People coming in and out.

583
01:03:51,420 --> 01:03:55,290
- 俄罗斯科学家  - 他们在干嘛？
- Russian scientists.  - Well, what are they up to?

584
01:03:55,760 --> 01:03:58,890
不知，他们在地下室，我不能去
They go in the basement and I'm not allowed in.

585
01:03:59,400 --> 01:04:02,300
现在是你设法进去的好时机
Now's a good time for you to get invited.

586
01:04:02,900 --> 01:04:08,900
尤里知道你是情报员，阿奇正在外面拿枪指着你
Yorgi knows you're an agent. Kirill is waiting with his rifle.

587
01:04:14,850 --> 01:04:16,340
- 哪里…？ - 别看！
- Where...?  - Don't look!

588
01:04:17,450 --> 01:04:19,420
这里有后门
There's a back door.

589
01:04:19,690 --> 01:04:21,850
走后门，他们就知道你警告我
They'll know you warned me.

590
01:04:22,020 --> 01:04:25,510
走前门，他就会射杀你
If you go out the front, he'll put a bullet in your eye.

591
01:04:36,100 --> 01:04:38,760
- 你有带枪吗？ - 一直都有
- You still packing?  - Always.

592
01:04:39,040 --> 01:04:40,900
准备用枪吧
Get ready to use it.

593
01:04:43,940 --> 01:04:46,970
- 你有何计划？ - 他还爱着你，对吧？
- What's your plan?  - He's still in love with you.

594
01:04:47,150 --> 01:04:52,520
- 除非有把握，他不会开枪  - 这就是你的计划？你还真行
- He'll wait for a clear shot.  - That's your plan? Thank you. Great.

595
01:05:16,840 --> 01:05:17,900
拔枪
Draw!

596
01:06:07,560 --> 01:06:09,420
他上路了
He's on the way.

597
01:06:47,100 --> 01:06:51,630
纪本，我最喜爱的绑匪头头，下回派辆礼车来接我吧
Gibbons! My favorite kidnapper. Next time send a limo.

598
01:06:58,940 --> 01:07:01,110
哇咧，你别闹了吧
Oh, you've got to be kidding me.

599
01:07:01,310 --> 01:07:05,440
你已打败我了，不用再折磨我
You already broke me. No need to get cruel and unusual.

600
01:07:08,950 --> 01:07:11,050
机票？这可好玩了
A ticket? Now, that's funny.

601
01:07:11,220 --> 01:07:13,820
- 我现在要去哪？ - 回家
- Where am I going to go now?  - Home.

602
01:07:14,630 --> 01:07:15,620
回家？
Home?

603
01:07:15,960 --> 01:07:18,230
你的身分已被揭穿，你没用了
Your cover's blown. You're not useful.

604
01:07:18,400 --> 01:07:19,730
就这样？没我的事了？
That's it? I'm done?

605
01:07:19,900 --> 01:07:23,530
没错，我们情报已足供进行下一步行动
No tricks. We have enough intel to move forward.

606
01:07:23,700 --> 01:07:28,570
- 谁去行动？ - 扫荡小组，快又有效
- With what?  - Sweeper team: quick, clean, effective.

607
01:07:28,740 --> 01:07:31,680
不用担心，事情很快就会解决
Don't worry about it. It'll all be over soon.

608
01:07:32,240 --> 01:07:35,580
你派扫荡小组去杀光所有人？
You mean a sweeper team to come in and kill everybody?

609
01:07:35,750 --> 01:07:38,510
他们并非全都是大坏蛋
Not all of them are as bad as you think.

610
01:07:38,680 --> 01:07:42,710
你得杀警才能混进去，他们这还不算是坏人？
You had to shoot a cop. How "not as bad as I think" could they be?

611
01:07:42,890 --> 01:07:45,050
好吧，听着
Okay, look.

612
01:07:45,290 --> 01:07:49,020
事情有点复杂，里面有个女人，约娜
We've got a complication. There's a girl. Yelena.

613
01:07:49,190 --> 01:07:50,680
永远都是有个女人
There's always a girl.

614
01:07:50,860 --> 01:07:54,890
她想逃出来，而我派她回去帮你搜集情报
She wants out and I sent her back in to get more intel for you.

615
01:07:55,070 --> 01:07:59,130
没时间玩游戏，决定已经下了
There's no time to play favorites. The cards have been dealt.

616
01:07:59,300 --> 01:08:01,970
什么叫决定已经下了？
What do you mean the cards have been dealt?

617
01:08:02,140 --> 01:08:04,440
你根本不认识她
You don't even know her, man.

618
01:08:06,040 --> 01:08:09,500
对了，你给我们的银行帐号
Oh, by the way, that bank number you gave us?

619
01:08:10,150 --> 01:08:15,810
你朋友和约娜，转帐大笔的现金…
Your friends and Yelena have made some large cash transfers...

620
01:08:16,020 --> 01:08:20,190
给一群俄罗斯科学家，他们专精于…
...to a group of Russian scientists known to specialize and traffic...

621
01:08:20,390 --> 01:08:22,990
生化武器
...in biological weapons.

622
01:08:23,600 --> 01:08:26,500
- 老大，她跟那没关系  - 回家吧
- She had nothing to do with it.  - Go home.

623
01:08:26,670 --> 01:08:28,600
- 她…  - 这是命令
- She ain't...!  - That's an order.

624
01:08:48,950 --> 01:08:49,940
情况如何？
How's it going?

625
01:08:50,120 --> 01:08:51,420
人生真烂！
Life is shit!

626
01:08:51,620 --> 01:08:53,450
是啊，但你又能如何？
Yeah, well what can you do?

627
01:10:47,010 --> 01:10:50,200
过了这扇门，你就要效忠到底
Through this door, you are with us to the end.

628
01:10:50,410 --> 01:10:53,710
- 你确定要这样？ - 我确定
- Are you sure that's what you want?  - I'm sure.

629
01:12:33,680 --> 01:12:38,340
这是亚哈号，它就像是艘太阳能潜水艇
This is Ahab. Think of it as solar-powered submarine.

630
01:12:38,580 --> 01:12:41,520
它能绕行全球，命中目标
It can circumnavigate the globe to reach its target.

631
01:12:41,750 --> 01:12:46,620
它只需要在水面上搜集阳光，就能完成任务
It need only surface to gather sunshine and to do its business.

632
01:12:47,030 --> 01:12:49,720
什么任务？
What is it? What's its business?

633
01:12:50,160 --> 01:12:55,220
送礼物给乖小孩
Dropping off presents to all the good little boys and girls.

634
01:13:04,810 --> 01:13:07,870
我们明天就可以完成
My team will be finished tomorrow.

635
01:13:08,450 --> 01:13:09,440
你们呢？
How about you?

636
01:13:10,480 --> 01:13:13,280
我们好了
We're finished now.

637
01:13:45,120 --> 01:13:46,170
尼可莱！
Nikolai!

638
01:13:46,480 --> 01:13:48,480
准备火箭
Bring the rockets.

639
01:13:56,300 --> 01:13:57,150
[亚哈号]

640
01:14:25,720 --> 01:14:28,590
给你设定
The detonator is for you.

641
01:15:18,480 --> 01:15:20,810
毒气开始混合…
Yorgi! The binary agents are mixing...

642
01:15:20,980 --> 01:15:23,070
会害死大家！
...it will kill us all!

643
01:15:33,260 --> 01:15:35,780
看起来真像小白鼠
Looks like little white mouse.

644
01:15:39,300 --> 01:15:41,130
拜拜，小白鼠
Bye-bye, little mouse.

645
01:15:58,850 --> 01:16:00,280
天啊
My God.

646
01:17:01,880 --> 01:17:05,940
他们的工作已经完成，现在他们成了累赘
They did their job and now they were liability.

647
01:17:06,920 --> 01:17:10,620
我们不需要太多知情的人
We don't need anyone talking about our business.

648
01:17:15,990 --> 01:17:20,660
风扇会抽出毒气，让它通过水
The gas gets sucked through the extractor fans, passed into water...

649
01:17:20,830 --> 01:17:24,790
再转化为完全无毒的空气
...and broken down to become, once again, completely harmless.

650
01:17:28,570 --> 01:17:30,470
真安静
So quiet.

651
01:17:33,410 --> 01:17:37,210
难怪它会被称为“寂静之夜”
I know now why they call it Silent Night.

652
01:17:45,890 --> 01:17:47,320
去吃点东西
Let's get some food.

653
01:18:22,630 --> 01:18:24,560
快去查是怎么回事
Find out what's going on!

654
01:18:58,830 --> 01:19:00,020
搞什么？
What the hell was that?

655
01:19:06,700 --> 01:19:08,230
这招管用
That works.

656
01:20:35,340 --> 01:20:36,770
引爆
Fire in the hole.

657
01:21:06,140 --> 01:21:09,070
你怎么会在这里？
Sova. What are you doing here, man?

658
01:21:09,240 --> 01:21:12,700
你先是在酒吧里陷害我，接着又开枪杀我
First you set me up in the bar. Then you shoot me in the back.

659
01:21:12,880 --> 01:21:16,570
我老板这么对我，我再这么对你，这是恶性循环
My boss does it to me. I did it to you. It's a vicious circle.

660
01:21:16,780 --> 01:21:18,440
- 你觉得这很有趣？ - 不，我不觉得
- You think it's funny?  - No.

661
01:21:18,620 --> 01:21:21,310
你不会是怀恨在心吧？
You didn't take it personally, did you?

662
01:21:21,520 --> 01:21:25,180
我设法混进去，我们是站同一边的，记得吧？
I did what I had to do to get in. We're on the same side.

663
01:21:25,360 --> 01:21:28,260
抱歉，我换边了
I'm sorry. I switched sides.

664
01:21:28,790 --> 01:21:33,230
你对我太过份了，我的政府给的也没尤里多
You pushed me too far. My government doesn't pay as well as Yorgi.

665
01:21:34,200 --> 01:21:36,430
我的政府给的是尤里给的两倍…
My government pays twice as much...

666
01:21:36,630 --> 01:21:39,360
你以为这样突然跳进来这行…
Think you could just walk into the spy business...

667
01:21:39,540 --> 01:21:44,700
- 就能一切顺风如意？ - 那你要怎样？射杀我？
- ...and have all the angles figured out?  - What are you going to do, shoot me?

668
01:21:44,880 --> 01:21:46,900
你希望我射哪里？头？
Where? In the head, to be quick?

669
01:21:47,080 --> 01:21:50,450
还是胸，好让我看看你的心脏
Or in the chest for an open casket, so I can see your heart?

670
01:21:50,650 --> 01:21:52,640
我想一下
Can I think about it?

671
01:22:00,690 --> 01:22:02,020
你这是干嘛？
What are you doing?!

672
01:22:02,190 --> 01:22:06,100
我听到你讲话，知道你在哪里
I heard you talking. I could tell where you were in the room.

673
01:22:07,770 --> 01:22:10,260
你怎么会跟伊凡在一起？
What are you doing with the lvans?

674
01:22:14,210 --> 01:22:15,330
怎么回事？
What's going on?

675
01:22:15,510 --> 01:22:19,000
我有些话之前没对你说
There's something I didn't have the time to tell you.

676
01:22:19,180 --> 01:22:21,240
我也是个情报员
I'm an agent as well.

677
01:22:21,410 --> 01:22:24,850
我是俄罗斯情报局的探员
I'm an agent for FSB, Russian Intelligence.

678
01:22:25,020 --> 01:22:27,080
很像你们的中情局
You know, like your CIA.

679
01:22:27,250 --> 01:22:30,240
- 我卧底两年了  - 两年？
- I've been undercover for two years.  - Two years?

680
01:22:30,420 --> 01:22:33,150
你的计划是什么？等他们老死吗？
What was your plan, let them die of old age?

681
01:22:33,360 --> 01:22:34,720
我们根本没有计划
There was no plan.

682
01:22:34,890 --> 01:22:39,490
一年半以前，局里改组，我不再收到指令
A year ago, Intelligence gets reorganized, I stop getting orders.

683
01:22:39,860 --> 01:22:44,490
他们把我给忘了，我只能尽力求生，你懂吗？
They forget about me. And I did what I must to survive. You understand?

684
01:22:44,700 --> 01:22:47,970
我懂个屁，我才入行一周而已
What do I understand? I've been an agent for a week.

685
01:22:48,140 --> 01:22:51,110
但我老板得知道一切详情
But my boss needs to know what we know now.

686
01:22:51,280 --> 01:22:54,070
- 好吗？ - 好
- Okay?  - Okay.

687
01:22:55,150 --> 01:22:59,280
潜艇会施放神经毒气“寂静之夜”
The submarine's purpose is to deploy a nerve agent called Silent Night.

688
01:22:59,450 --> 01:23:02,680
它的配方在苏联解体后就失踪
It's been missing since the Soviet Union's collapse in '91 .

689
01:23:02,850 --> 01:23:04,190
它能屠杀百万人口
It can kill millions.

690
01:23:04,360 --> 01:23:07,450
我们早知他们有鬼，你查到了
We knew they were up to something. You found out.

691
01:23:07,630 --> 01:23:11,820
- 干的好，XXX  - 原来根本没什么扫荡小组
- That's excellent work, Triple X.  - There was never a sweeper team.

692
01:23:13,360 --> 01:23:16,330
我若叫你别去跳帝国大厦…
If I said don't jump off the Empire State Building....

693
01:23:16,530 --> 01:23:19,900
- 没错，我铁定会去跳  - 我激励了你
- You're right. I'd definitely do it.  - I inspired you.

694
01:23:20,070 --> 01:23:23,560
看吧，我是掌权者，我理当这么做
I'm an authority figure, that's what I'm supposed to do.

695
01:23:23,740 --> 01:23:25,770
听着，我的人已经接手
Look, my men are on this now.

696
01:23:25,940 --> 01:23:29,350
- 你该回家了  - 那约娜呢？
- It's time for you to come home.  - What about Yelena?

697
01:23:32,720 --> 01:23:35,780
我无权给她庇护
I'm not authorized to give her asylum.

698
01:23:37,220 --> 01:23:40,450
但我保证你回来时一定搞定
But I promise it'll be done by the time you get here.

699
01:23:41,890 --> 01:23:44,920
回来吧，桑德，这是命令
Come home, Xander. That's an order.

700
01:24:01,810 --> 01:24:04,610
尤里多快就能发射这玩意？
How soon can Yorgi launch this thing?

701
01:24:08,350 --> 01:24:11,650
他们叫你回去，你们的人接手…
You were told to go home! Your people are handling...

702
01:24:11,860 --> 01:24:13,760
多快？
How soon, Yelena?

703
01:24:16,260 --> 01:24:18,890
很快，但这不关我们的事了
Soon. But it's not our problem anymore!

704
01:24:19,100 --> 01:24:22,000
他们若提前行动，就事关重大
If they get ahead of schedule, it's everyone's.

705
01:24:22,170 --> 01:24:26,500
不可能的，他有军队、碉堡，你根本没有机会
He's got an army, a fortress. You don't stand a chance!

706
01:24:26,670 --> 01:24:31,470
我曾为很多蠢事冒险，这是第一件对我有意义的事
I've risked my life for stupid reasons. This is the first one that makes sense.

707
01:24:31,680 --> 01:24:36,170
这不是特技表演，你会送命的
This is not one of your stunts. You'll die in this, you know that.

708
01:24:38,620 --> 01:24:41,020
我知道你若没回去…
If you don't go back in there...

709
01:24:42,820 --> 01:24:45,310
他就会知道出事了
...he'll know something's wrong.

710
01:24:45,490 --> 01:24:49,220
你不能要我回去，不行
You can't ask me to go back there. You can't.

711
01:24:52,130 --> 01:24:56,970
知道最讽刺的是什么吗？我是自愿争取这任务的
You want to know something ironic? I volunteered for this assignment.

712
01:24:58,340 --> 01:25:01,100
我想有所贡献
I wanted to make a difference.

713
01:25:02,210 --> 01:25:03,870
我努力争取这任务
I fought for it.

714
01:25:07,650 --> 01:25:08,940
那就完成它
Then finish it.

715
01:25:26,660 --> 01:25:29,900
记得你吻我之后，我说了什么？
Remember what I told you, after you kissed me?

716
01:25:30,340 --> 01:25:32,900
- 没有下次？ - 我说谎
- Never again?  - I lied.

717
01:25:51,390 --> 01:25:54,620
你仔细分析，其实我很单纯
But when you break it down, I'm a simple man.

718
01:25:54,790 --> 01:25:56,950
我很高兴能跟捷克美女…
I'd be happy with a beautiful Czech girl...

719
01:25:57,160 --> 01:26:01,120
怪胎！纪本下了新指令，上车
Hey, geek! Got new orders from Gibbons. Get in.

720
01:26:06,200 --> 01:26:09,470
- 我要那些全装进这车里  - 没问题
- I want all that in here.  - Done.

721
01:26:09,640 --> 01:26:13,040
城堡到处装满监视器
The castle's covered with surveillance cameras.

722
01:26:14,150 --> 01:26:16,740
所以我们才无法靠近
That's why we cannot get close enough.

723
01:26:19,120 --> 01:26:24,580
等等，所以我要去摧毁山脚下的…
Hang on. That's why I need to knock out the communications tower...

724
01:26:24,760 --> 01:26:26,820
联络塔
...at the base of the mountain.

725
01:26:32,460 --> 01:26:35,630
这里有人会开飞机吗？
Is there anyone here who knows how to fly a plane?

726
01:26:36,900 --> 01:26:38,230
我会
I can.

727
01:26:45,480 --> 01:26:48,140
这些山峰附近乱流太多
Too much turbulence around these mountains!

728
01:26:48,350 --> 01:26:50,970
把我送到那个塔上方就好
Just get me in line with that tower!

729
01:26:51,150 --> 01:26:52,710
剩下的交给我
I'll do the rest!

730
01:27:06,500 --> 01:27:07,490
跳吧
Go now!

731
01:28:29,580 --> 01:28:30,910
维多，有访客来了！
Viktor! We got company!

732
01:28:35,750 --> 01:28:38,720
活逮他，再好好折磨他！
Catch him fast. Kill him slow!

733
01:32:29,250 --> 01:32:31,050
新鲜的雪花真棒
Nothing like fresh powder.

734
01:33:07,960 --> 01:33:12,120
老相好，你是不是头昏了？
Yelena, my sweet dove, did you get confused?

735
01:33:12,530 --> 01:33:17,260
你的任务是那条子杀了桑德后，再杀了他
Your assignment was to kill the cop after he killed X.

736
01:33:18,270 --> 01:33:22,710
这样不是个好俄罗斯卧底密探
Not good for undercover agent from Russian Intelligence.

737
01:33:27,380 --> 01:33:30,310
我一直都知道你的底细…
I knew about you all along...

738
01:33:30,480 --> 01:33:35,610
能随意摆布并利用你，真是好玩
...and it was my pleasure to twist you and use you how I saw fit.

739
01:33:37,450 --> 01:33:38,680
还有你
And you.

740
01:33:43,660 --> 01:33:46,490
在众人之中，我以为你会懂…
Of all people, I thought you'd understand...

741
01:33:46,700 --> 01:33:49,060
我想达成的梦想
...what I'm trying to accomplish.

742
01:33:49,570 --> 01:33:51,500
你想像一下？
Can you imagine?

743
01:33:52,240 --> 01:33:55,300
想像布拉格在毒气云团下…
Imagine a city like Prague vanishing...

744
01:33:55,510 --> 01:33:58,480
被消灭殆尽
...in a cloud of poison gas.

745
01:33:58,640 --> 01:34:01,980
还有汉堡、伦敦、华盛顿
Then Hamburg, London, Washington.

746
01:34:02,480 --> 01:34:07,780
凶手不明，原因也不明，所以大家兵戎相见
Imagine not knowing who did it, or why. And so they turn on each other.

747
01:34:08,190 --> 01:34:12,120
这些人攻击那些人，那些人侵略这些人
These guys attack those guys. Those guys invade these guys.

748
01:34:12,290 --> 01:34:15,260
很快地，全世界闹内讧
Soon, whole world implodes.

749
01:34:15,430 --> 01:34:18,620
政府全都消失
Imagine governments disappearing.

750
01:34:18,800 --> 01:34:20,590
最后…
And in the end...

751
01:34:20,760 --> 01:34:25,290
达成一个绝对完美的自由状态
...imagine facing absolute, beautiful freedom.

752
01:34:29,840 --> 01:34:33,040
但你们都无缘亲眼目睹了
But neither of you will be there to see it.

753
01:34:35,180 --> 01:34:37,200
跟维多一样
Like Viktor.

754
01:34:40,120 --> 01:34:41,780
还有柯亚
Like Kolya.

755
01:35:28,430 --> 01:35:30,060
掩护我
Cover me!

756
01:35:39,580 --> 01:35:41,670
帮我解开
Get me out of this thing!

757
01:35:45,850 --> 01:35:49,110
他拿走硬碟，他要发射亚哈号
He took the hard drive. He's going to launch Ahab!

758
01:35:55,160 --> 01:35:56,960
自己选
Pick one.

759
01:36:07,670 --> 01:36:09,260
伊凡，轰了那些狙击手！
Ivan, take out that nest!

760
01:36:30,160 --> 01:36:32,090
你要扳开保险才行
You have to turn the safety off.

761
01:36:56,120 --> 01:36:58,280
尽量拖住他们
Hold them off as long as you can.

762
01:37:00,060 --> 01:37:01,960
再见了，朋友
See you, my friend.

763
01:37:58,620 --> 01:38:00,280
快啊
Come on, baby.

764
01:38:08,960 --> 01:38:11,930
停！他困住我们了
Stop! He's got us pinned down.

765
01:38:15,800 --> 01:38:17,270
该死
Shit.

766
01:38:17,600 --> 01:38:19,190
你有火箭筒啊
You got a bazooka!

767
01:38:19,370 --> 01:38:23,600
别把自己当警察，当电玩高手，随便开轰啊
Stop thinking Prague police and start thinking PlayStation. Blow shit up!

768
01:38:23,810 --> 01:38:27,300
这不是火箭筒，这是热感火箭
This is not bazooka. This is heat-seeker rocket.

769
01:38:29,880 --> 01:38:31,250
感热？
Heat-seeker?

770
01:38:32,720 --> 01:38:33,740
架好它
Set it.

771
01:38:38,260 --> 01:38:40,750
那痞子在抽烟
The son of a bitch is smoking.

772
01:38:57,540 --> 01:39:00,410
我说过他会被烟害死，走吧
I told him that cigarette would kill him.

773
01:40:01,440 --> 01:40:03,700
学学怎么开枪吧，笨蛋
Learn how to shoot, piece of shit!

774
01:40:29,230 --> 01:40:31,670
快，帮我把他拉出来
Quick! Help me pull him out!

775
01:40:36,210 --> 01:40:38,440
那玩意半小时内会抵达市内
It will hit the city in 30 minutes!

776
01:40:53,060 --> 01:40:55,550
各位，我需要直升机
Guys. I need a helicopter.

777
01:40:56,360 --> 01:40:58,620
我需要交通工具，我需要…
I need transportation. I need a...

778
01:41:05,700 --> 01:41:09,330
你在这，我在找你，一切搞定
X, there you are. I gave you everything you wanted.

779
01:41:09,510 --> 01:41:11,670
这玩意只差不会飞了
This thing will damn near fly now.

780
01:41:11,840 --> 01:41:14,740
你耍我，纪本根本没下令
You screwed me. Gibbons didn't authorize this.

781
01:41:14,910 --> 01:41:16,740
他会整死我们，我会完蛋
He'll hang us both out to dry.

782
01:41:16,910 --> 01:41:18,780
- 托比探员  - 什么事？
- Agent Shavers.  - Yeah?

783
01:41:19,080 --> 01:41:21,850
我要升你的职
I'm going to give you a field promotion.

784
01:41:22,020 --> 01:41:25,510
接手这个现场，由你全权负责
Take over, finish the mop-up. You're in charge.

785
01:41:26,160 --> 01:41:30,060
遵命，我保证达成任务，我决不会令你失望
Yes, sir! I'm the man for the job! I won't let you down!

786
01:41:31,230 --> 01:41:32,920
等等、等等
Wait! Wait! Wait!

787
01:41:33,530 --> 01:41:35,230
操作手册，你会需要的
Almost forgot the manual. You'll need this.

788
01:41:35,430 --> 01:41:38,130
老大，去拯救世界吧
Hey, X. Go kick some ass.

789
01:41:59,060 --> 01:42:03,150
那玩意时速肯定有八十哩，我们要怎么停下它？
That thing must be going 80 mph! How do we stop it?!

790
01:42:03,360 --> 01:42:07,390
没办法，控制中心在上面的透明圆顶里
We can't! The controls are on the bubble panel.

791
01:42:07,560 --> 01:42:09,260
- 看到了？ - 看到了
- You see it?  - Yeah.

792
01:42:09,430 --> 01:42:11,660
硬碟就在里面
The hard drive's in there!

793
01:42:11,840 --> 01:42:16,200
你有操作手册，查一查有什么可用的机关
You got the manual. See if Shavers put in anything we could use.

794
01:42:16,370 --> 01:42:19,370
- 他的字迹很潦草  - 快点
- He's got very bad handwriting.  - Come on!

795
01:42:19,710 --> 01:42:24,980
火焰喷射器、迷你炸弹、车轮盖炸弹、火箭发射器
Flame throwers, mini-bombs, exploding hubcaps, rocket launchers!

796
01:42:25,580 --> 01:42:29,210
这是辆坦克，你不能拿它对付亚哈号
This is a tank. You can't use any of it on Ahab.

797
01:42:29,390 --> 01:42:32,980
寂静之夜要在深水中引爆才行
Silent Night only breaks down in deep water.

798
01:42:33,890 --> 01:42:36,020
- 我要上去  - 什么？
- I'll have to get on it!  - What?

799
01:42:37,490 --> 01:42:39,290
我要上去
I'll have to get on it.

800
01:42:46,500 --> 01:42:51,070
亚哈号再二十二分就到达布拉格了
Our surveillance puts Ahab 22 minutes outside of Prague.

801
01:42:51,270 --> 01:42:55,970
- 我们该疏散整个城市  - 二十二分钟疏散一百五十万人？
- We should evacuate the city.  - 22 minutes for 1.5 million people?

802
01:42:56,310 --> 01:42:59,940
找空军支援，我们可能得在水面上炸了它
Call air support. We may need to blow it out of the water.

803
01:43:00,380 --> 01:43:03,180
- 要是我们击中它…  - 那整个城市就完了
- lf we hit that thing...  - This city will die.

804
01:43:03,350 --> 01:43:05,480
危机必须受到控制
And the crisis will be contained!

805
01:43:05,660 --> 01:43:07,420
牺牲一个城市总胜过十个
One city's better than 10.

806
01:43:09,990 --> 01:43:13,550
还有一件事，有辆跑车跟亚哈号并行前进
Another thing: A blue GTO is traveling parallel to Ahab.

807
01:43:25,110 --> 01:43:27,910
该死，这条路会回到河边吗？
Shit! Does this road go back to the river?

808
01:43:28,310 --> 01:43:30,680
快点，查导航地图啊
Come on! Check the GPS!

809
01:43:32,420 --> 01:43:35,870
会！在十五哩后的狄维镇！
Yes, it does! Fifteen miles at the town of Davle!

810
01:43:53,470 --> 01:43:56,460
这里一定有我们能用的东西
There's got to be something here we could use.

811
01:43:56,640 --> 01:44:00,670
鱼叉炮、降落伞座椅、可弹射车顶
Harpoon gun, parachutes built into seats, ejectable roof.

812
01:44:00,840 --> 01:44:03,010
全都没用
It's all useless!

813
01:44:04,480 --> 01:44:05,780
还有多远？
How far are we?

814
01:44:07,520 --> 01:44:10,540
那河就在下个村落后面
The river is just beyond the next village.

815
01:44:19,700 --> 01:44:22,760
我要直接冲过去，发射火箭
I'm going through! Use the rocket launcher!

816
01:44:22,930 --> 01:44:24,630
- 二十二号！ - 快按
- Twenty-two!  - Hit it!

817
01:44:28,210 --> 01:44:30,700
那是火焰发射器，用火箭
That was a flamethrower! Use the rockets!

818
01:44:30,870 --> 01:44:34,070
是三十二号，我说过了，我说过他字迹很潦草
It's 32! I told you! I told you he had bad handwriting!

819
01:44:34,240 --> 01:44:35,400
快按
Hit it!

820
01:45:09,810 --> 01:45:13,680
托比全都装上来了，查手册，我们一定漏了什么
Shavers loaded this thing. We're missing something.

821
01:45:13,980 --> 01:45:16,850
后面有更多武器，你看
There are more weapons here on the back. Look.

822
01:45:27,400 --> 01:45:31,530
- 你来开车！ - 什么？你疯了
- Take the wheel!  - What? You're crazy!

823
01:45:36,210 --> 01:45:37,570
刹车！刹车！
The brake! The brake!

824
01:45:40,510 --> 01:45:41,770
加油！加油！
The gas! The gas!

825
01:45:54,960 --> 01:45:56,430
你在干嘛？
X, what are you doing?

826
01:45:57,290 --> 01:45:59,160
五分钟后抵达目标上空
Five minutes to target.

827
01:46:04,600 --> 01:46:06,690
说话啊，你在干嘛？
X, talk to me! What are you doing?

828
01:46:07,040 --> 01:46:10,030
- 你说过有个可弹射车顶  - 对，就是那里
- You said there was an ejectable roof.  - Right here!

829
01:46:10,210 --> 01:46:11,260
按下去！
Hit it!

830
01:46:25,390 --> 01:46:27,950
该死，太远了
Shit! It's out of range!

831
01:46:28,120 --> 01:46:31,560
- 那里有座桥，过桥去！ - 好
- There's a bridge! Cross the bridge!  - Okay.

832
01:46:46,280 --> 01:46:47,370
加油
Come on.

833
01:46:50,950 --> 01:46:52,040
加油
Come on!

834
01:46:54,420 --> 01:46:56,780
- 中了！ - 好耶！
- Got you!  - Yes!

835
01:46:58,490 --> 01:47:01,480
- 我真希望有带摄影机！ - 你说什么？
- I wish I had a camera!  - What you talking about?

836
01:47:01,660 --> 01:47:04,150
因为这次的特技肯定炫毙了
This is gonna be one hell of a trick.

837
01:47:59,620 --> 01:48:01,280
三分钟后抵达
Three minutes to target.

838
01:49:53,160 --> 01:49:54,790
一分钟后抵达
One minute to target.

839
01:49:55,370 --> 01:49:57,490
快、快
Move! Move! Move!

840
01:49:58,470 --> 01:49:59,940
快让开、让开
Out of the way!

841
01:50:18,960 --> 01:50:20,220
望远镜
Eyes!

842
01:50:37,140 --> 01:50:38,900
十秒后抵达
Ten seconds to target.

843
01:50:47,950 --> 01:50:49,440
目标在望
Target in sight.

844
01:50:49,750 --> 01:50:53,650
取消空中行动，叫战机撤退
Call the jets off. Tell the jets to stand down!

845
01:51:06,540 --> 01:51:08,970
欢迎进入桑德特区
Welcome to the Xander zone!

846
01:51:49,310 --> 01:51:54,650
零污染，我明白，长官，零污染
Zero contamination level. I understand, sir. Zero contamination level.

847
01:52:06,200 --> 01:52:07,320
你就是约娜？
You Yelena?

848
01:52:08,730 --> 01:52:10,430
纪本先生
Mr. Gibbons.

849
01:52:11,230 --> 01:52:14,000
我答应桑德要让你去美国
I promised Xander you could go to America.

850
01:52:14,600 --> 01:52:16,400
我言出必行
I'm a man of my word.

851
01:52:16,570 --> 01:52:19,510
现在这也没什么意义了
It doesn't make much difference now, does it?

852
01:52:45,440 --> 01:52:48,630
他还活着，快过来
He's alive! He's alive! Come here!

853
01:52:55,780 --> 01:52:59,840
快把他弄回来，快，快去
